ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m tra s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i v\u00e0 ni\u00eam phong c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng h\u00f3a. Tuy nhi\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c ki\u1ec3m tra ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m b\u00ean trong (th\u1eed \u0111\u1ed3, test m\u00e1y&#8230;) th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p, tr\u1eeb khi c\u00f3 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1eefa ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e1n th\u00f4ng qua \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n. Quy \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y gi\u00fap tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng tranh ch\u1ea5p kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5594\" src=\"https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Vay-Ship-cod-co-duoc-kiem-tra-hang-khong-.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"V\u1eady Ship cod c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3m tra h\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Vay-Ship-cod-co-duoc-kiem-tra-hang-khong-.jpg 800w, https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Vay-Ship-cod-co-duoc-kiem-tra-hang-khong--300x188.jpg 300w, https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Vay-Ship-cod-co-duoc-kiem-tra-hang-khong--768x480.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><strong>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u01b0u \u00fd khi ki\u1ec3m tra h\u00e0ng khi n\u200bh\u1eadn Ship COD<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ki\u1ec3m tra h\u00e0ng COD di\u1ec5n ra thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i v\u00e0 tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3, c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e1n c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau:<\/p>\n<p><em>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua:<\/em><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>N\u00ean ki\u1ec3m tra k\u1ef9 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i v\u00e0 ni\u00eam phong c\u1ee7a h\u